Package com.smsapp.model

Class Student

java.lang.Object
com.smsapp.model.Student
public class Student extends Object
Represents a student in the School Management System.

This class provides the necessary fields and methods to manage student information, including personal details, contact information, assigned teachers, and enrolled exams.

Author:
MonigaBalasubramanian

      public Student(int studentId, String studentName, Date dateOfBirth, Date dateOfJoining, int parentContact, Address address, String mailId, Gender gender, BloodGroup bloodGroup, int grade, String house, List<Teacher> teachersAssigned, List<Exam> exams)
      Parameterized constructor to initialize a student object with the provided values.
      Parameters:
      studentId - the unique ID of the student
      studentName - the name of the student
      dateOfBirth - the birth date of the student
      dateOfJoining - the joining date of the student
      parentContact - the contact number of the student's parent
      address - the address of the student
      mailId - the email ID of the student
      gender - the gender of the student
      bloodGroup - the blood group of the student
      grade - the grade/class of the student
      house - the house assigned to the student
      teachersAssigned - the list of teachers assigned to the student
      exams - the list of exams the student is enrolled in
